# Banking Application Test Plan

## Objective
Verify that the online banking application functions correctly and securely.

## Scope
- Login
- Dashboard
- Balance Inquiry
- Fund Transfer
- Bill Payment
- Transaction History

## Test Types
- Functional Testing
- Regression Testing
- Smoke Testing
- Negative Testing
- UI Testing

## Test Environment
- Windows 11
- Chrome
- Microsoft Edge

## Exit Criteria
- All critical defects resolved.
- All high-priority test cases pass.
